{"id":370076,"date":[{"year":1958,"month":6,"day":4}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"440","ytitle":"","mtitle":"东风永远压西风(弹词开篇)","ftitle":"","authors":["灵犀"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风今日压西风，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胜利的红旗满天空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国际形势分优劣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和平阵容力量宏；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义路已穷。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(我们是)人民民主团结紧；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(他们是)矛盾重重闹得凶。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被压迫(的)民族齐奋起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"政治斗争气势雄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫和平反侵略，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风今日压西风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(苏联的)第三颗卫星吨半重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乘东风，上九重。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红光灿烂耀长虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(还打算)访问嫦娥(到)广寒宫。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(可笑它)美国卫星拳头大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还将神像供当中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(但愿得)上帝向导多保佑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一路顺风上天空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(那知道)上天无路翻筋斗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一去茫茫无影踪；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风今日压西风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大英帝国黄昏近，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(法国是)风雨飘摇路不通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(美国的)经济危机尤严重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"剜肉补疮国库空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"狼狈不堪尼克松。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(苏联是)生产年年超美国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(在那)和平经济竞赛中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"定操胜数显神通。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(再看我们)中华人民共和国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经济建设日繁荣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(要争取)主要工业超英国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不消十五载，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一定能成功，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纷纷传捷报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"处处出英雄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"创造奇迹满堂红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东风今日压西风。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中共八大代表会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鼓舞人心向前冲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义建设总路线，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万道光芒映日红；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(从此是)东风永远压西风。"}]}